# Carriage templates bundled into the mod jar.
#
# Files here are consumed by CarriageTemplateStore.loadFromResource at
# /data/dungeontrain/templates/<carriage_type>.nbt. They are produced by:
#   - /dungeontrain editor devmode on, then /dungeontrain editor save
#   - /dungeontrain editor promote <variant>
#   - /dungeontrain editor promote all
#
# Both paths only succeed in a ./gradlew runClient dev session.
